Class SwfActionContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • flash.swf.TagHandler
      • flash.tools.SwfActionContainer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LineFunctionContainer

    public class SwfActionContainer
extends flash.swf.TagHandler
    This class implements the TagHandler interface and provides a mechanism for containing the actions associated with a SWF.
